You're absolutely right,

798
01:03:35,231 --> 01:03:38,313
5099 has to what's
best for the family.

799
01:03:38,398 --> 01:03:41,342
He has to leave or
else they're in danger.

800
01:03:42,483 --> 01:03:43,678
