of days, Harold see you soon.

818
01:04:26,067 --> 01:04:27,060
Kyle.

819
01:04:27,809 --> 01:04:28,615
Sir.

820
01:04:28,700 --> 01:04:30,693
That is one ballsy
client you have there,

821
01:04:31,159 --> 01:04:32,355
I like him.

822
01:04:33,615 --> 01:04:34,599
Thank you.

823
01:04:35,838 --> 01:04:37,053
Trevor!

824
01:04:38,454 --> 01:04:40,459
Iced green tea.
No sweetener.

825
01:04:40,544 --> 01:04:41,404
Yes sir.

826
