No sweetener.

827
01:04:43,535 --> 01:04:44,909
Would you like a drink?

828
01:04:44,994 --> 01:04:47,982
He did it.
That son of a gun did it.

829
01:04:51,283 --> 01:04:53,459
-Hey hey!
