833
01:05:02,618 --> 01:05:03,857
Well hurry up!

834
01:05:08,634 --> 01:05:10,466
He's not coming is he.

835
01:05:12,733 --> 01:05:14,842
Just do the best
you can without him.

836
01:05:19,822 --> 01:05:20,990
