01:05:48,395 --> 01:05:53,353
Hey I'm here! Alyssa!
Makayla, what can I help with?

838
01:06:56,494 --> 01:06:58,869
I read your script
babe, it's amazing.

839
01:06:59,431 --> 01:07:00,334
Go to your room.

840
01:07:00,419 --> 01:07:03,205
No no no,
please stay. I'm here ok,

841
01:07:04,069 --> 01:07:06,494
look, I know I
messed up, Alyssa?

842
01:07:15,158 --> 01:07:17,502
I can't wait to
see your movie babe.

843
01:07:18,462 --> 01:07:21,064
Hmmm. Going to my room now.

844
01:08:19,898 --> 01:08:21,117
Hey dad...

845
01:08:21,779 --> 01:08:22,851
Hey...

846
01:08:28,445 --> 01:08:30,202
