852
01:08:49,152 --> 01:08:50,109
Deal.

853
01:08:50,194 --> 01:08:51,656
Ok, lets go.

854
01:09:28,517 --> 01:09:34,808
Huh, oh my gosh,
this is good, this is good.

855
01:09:35,882 --> 01:09:38,562
You think it's this
easy to stroll in like this!?

856
01:09:38,913 --> 01:09:39,943
Hey...

857
01:09:41,835 --> 01:09:44,155
I was just about to
read her my script

858
01:09:44,240 --> 01:09:45,820
if you wanted to join us?

859
01:09:46,106 --> 01:09:48,374
Don't act like
you're out of the woods yet!

860
01:09:52,681 --> 01:09:54,343
At least I've landed.

861
01:10:40,983 --> 01:10:42,816
He pants and
looks around the beach,

862
01:10:42,900 --> 01:10:44,482
bits of wreckage
from his craft scatter

863
01:10:44,566 --> 01:10:46,878
the sand. Some
large, some small.

864
01:10:47,233 --> 01:10:50,066
Slowly calming, he looks
ahead and sees in front of him,

865
01:10:50,150 --> 01:10:54,098
a tall mountain of
sand. He studies it,

866
01:10:54,183 --> 01:10:57,191
then drops to his knees,
face whitening with desperation.

867
01:10:57,275 --> 01:11:01,487
He blinks and seems to be
clearly contemplating his situation.

868
01:11:01,605 --> 01:11:05,783
He lifts his arm and starts hitting
a cracked touch pad on his wrist.

869
01:11:06,292 --> 01:11:08,870
It finally comes
to life, sort of.

870
01:11:09,230 --> 01:11:10,737
He speaks into it.

871
01:11:11,696 --> 01:11:12,847
Control...

872
01:11:13,667 --> 01:11:16,128
do you read me Control?

873
01:11:17,210 --> 01:11:18,714
Please send rescue.
